snippet.title: Sockventure Official Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Available now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1222340/Sockventure/

In this challenging 2D platformer game, play as a Superhero and help the Kid to find all the missing socks inside the cursed washing machine. 

Sockventure has stunning colorful graphics, hand-crafted levels, tight controls and fun ever-changing gameplay.

NEVER MISS OUT ON NEWS!
